@anchor{Function drei-core:indent-region}
@deffn {Function} {drei-core:indent-region} view mark1 mark2
@findex drei-core:indent-region
Indent all lines in the region delimited by @code{mark1} and
@code{mark2} according to the rules of the active syntax in
@code{drei}. @code{mark1} and @code{mark2} will not be modified by this
function.
@end deffn
